    { "action": "ExitDialogueCooldown", "reason": "Do not contact me again for now." }
  ]
}
```
IMPORTANT: Use EXACTLY the format above. 'actions' must be an array of objects. Only include fields that have non-zero changes. If no effects occur, you may omit the JSON block.



